Package gobblin.publisher

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UnpublishedHandling
    DataPublishers implementing this interface will cause Gobblin to call UnpublishedHandling.handleUnpublishedWorkUnits(java.util.Collection<? extends gobblin.configuration.WorkUnitState>) if it determines the job will not be published.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataPublisher
    Defines how to publish data and its corresponding metadata.
    SingleTaskDataPublisher
    A subclass of DataPublisher that can publish data of a single Task.
